# Incident Management Tools
# These tools are defined inline in the agent DSL files.
# This file serves as a tool registry reference for the v2 export format.

# Tools:
#   create_incident — Create a new incident with SLA deadlines
#   get_incident_timeline — Get the incident timeline and SLA status
#   generate_rca — Generate root cause analysis for an incident
#   update_incident_status — Update incident status
#   get_customer_impact — Assess customer and revenue impact of an incident
